title: Starting a Podcast
description:
When a couple decides to start a podcast, they get offers they can't believe.

Written by Brad Temple
Featuring Willy Appelman, Michael Delisle, Maya Deshmukh, Tessa Hersh, Tristan Griffin and Chrissy Shackelford
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
